Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼 有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該是我的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計還有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好傷勢沒大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方來正式委託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總之今天先好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天出來的診斷結果不錯的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}好漂亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜大人肯定又是第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥...美由？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二年的選舉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當選了學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈當了副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜則當了書記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聚集對我們三個忠實溫順的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結成了以學生會為名目的「白騎士」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快了 很快一切都要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我做到這份上很不可思議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想感謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天看上去都如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是正確的感情表現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 我會記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到椅子那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 那個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰 休想壞我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了軍方的委託太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不用顧及繪理的錢包而大展拳腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明從來就沒有顧及過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 以後幹什麼都不用負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 可以毫無顧忌地行動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能快速解決事件了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes！能解開謎底＆完美救出美少女們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 現在設備也萬全了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？設備？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關鎗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不過人家說「沒有許可不準開槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然裝上了就要開槍呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們啊 不洗澡就開不成會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身心都坦誠相對的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來護衛都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們可以捲鋪蓋回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能不能幫我照看那孩子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來啊 繪理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在可以功成身退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想奪走我的神秘謎團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 就算老天放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真海繪理也不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 我明白了 把前面遮一遮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 別亂來啊 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都大鬧過一場了 竟然還若無其事地過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒事的話 就回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始上課了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續妨礙我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命不保哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 現在到哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到正上方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好高 好小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐步降低高度 開始進行探測
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方還借了些拉風的「玩具」給我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 地底探測裝置值多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 給我認真拍好啊 要清晰無碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是在拍寫真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花憐 前往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 學姐也開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 學姐 請多加小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟樣子已經被人見過一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 因為我已經進行了完美的變裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能控制 跟上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有一瞬間 但是操場有條發光的線般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料洩漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要關掉引擎迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫降？你降去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華平安著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我這邊繼續執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜堂 操場 還有體育館的地下有構造物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當有規模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是設施 到底是用來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 就是巨型機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七神合體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在電視購物上買到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認真說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是巨型宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外星人在誘拐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是美少女失蹤事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了調查這個星球的生態系統 美少女們才會被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所看到的就是其中一種Cattle Mutilation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(*Cattle Mutilation 牛隻肢體被切除 多被認為是外星人進行的實驗)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 神秘事件狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那裡沒人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一隻老鼠都沒見到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房間裡面什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我也不知道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去 就像是搬走了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 沒有地方破損
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長射擊造成的彈痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子老師強行闖入的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都消失得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不在禮拜堂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去體育館看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Silver Eagle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行B計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我轉接高雷準將閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往地下的入口...嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有的 就在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不戰鬥就跑 很讓人介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是陷阱...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要闖一闖！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了 繪理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪理？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下無法通信麼...這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華 藍華 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 這可不是到了地下就會被隔斷的通信器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人為干擾麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華的聯絡中斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為你們的同伴的話身體能力會得到強化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有生體認證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是那麼的過激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.05,0:24:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.91,0:24:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能來到這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.40,0:26:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.83,0:26:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要結束的 是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.04,0:26:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你 Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.86,0:26:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero？


